data.description: Welcome home! This 3 bedroom 1 bath home offers a newer metal roof, newer furnace, recently updated bathroom, new water heater and hardwood floors!! Enjoy the large  in the living room with nice soft carpet. Eat in kitchen opens up to the living room. Flex room offers a nice place for storage. Large laundry room and a car and a half garage. Corner lot in a desired neighborhood. Schedule a showing today! This one won't last long!
